column5: I understand, I’m stuck in past and can’t figure a way out, no one gives a fuck there just a bunch of fugly bitches that hate me so I might kill myself
Being in the person’s shoes for real is what works
Enough sympathy! That shit is useless
The world tried to kill me hundreds of times because of its inferiority
I think you can still use the internet if you are dead
Don’t be scared it’s relieving to die because bad guys can’t fuck with you anymore
I feel condemned to living but it’s all the shit lying to me
